'''[[non]]-[[Newtonian]] [[fluid]]'''
#{{physics}} a fluid whose [[stress]] at each point is not [[linearly]] [[proportional]] to the [[strain]] [[rate]] at that point; i.e. its [[viscosity]] depends on the applied [[shear]] [[force]]
